      "content": "wait really? i thought it was just strain. do i definitely need to see a doctor though? i'm super busy with work this week and dont really have time for an appointment. if i just get some of those redness relief drops or even just use more of the lubricant, can't i just wait a few days to see if the yellow stuff goes away on its own?",
